msgid "AdwSteamGtk"
msgstr "AdwSteamGtk"

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:13
msgid "Give Steam the Adwaita treatment"
msgstr "Ri Steam an dyghtyans Adwaita"

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:14
#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:16
msgid "Foldex"
msgstr "Foldex"

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:25
msgid ""
"Make Steam look like it belongs on your computer. This app installs and "
"updates the Adwaita-for-Steam skin for you. It's as simple as this:"
msgstr ""
"Liwa Steam avel y longya yn dha amontyell. An app ma lea ha nowedhi an thema "
"Adwaita-rag-Steam rag hwi. Y yw dre sempel:"

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:30
msgid "Configure the skin to your liking"
msgstr "Dyllo an thema dhe'th discernyans"

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:31
msgid "Click the “Apply” button"
msgstr "Klyckyewgh an boton \"Gweytha\""

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:32
msgid "Restart Steam"
msgstr "Dasdalleth Steam"

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:34
msgid ""
"On startup, the app will automatically download any updates to the skin and "
"display a notification. Apply the skin again and restart Steam to take the "
"changes into use."
msgstr ""
"Dres dalleth, an app a wra iskarga awtomatek neb nowedhow thema ha displetya "
"unn messach. Dasgweytha an thema ha dastalleth Steam dhe devnydhya an "
"chanjyow."

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:38
msgid ""
"In order to get rounded corners on Steam, you will need to use the “Rounded "
"Window Corners” GNOME extension."
msgstr ""
"Rag kollenwel kernow krenn yn Steam, hwi res devnydhya an ystynnans GNOME "
"\"Kernow Fenester Krenn\"."

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:244
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "Penn Fenester"

#: data/io.github.Foldex.AdwSteamGtk.appdata.xml.in:248
msgid "Theme Preview"
msgstr "Ragwolok Thema"

